375
00:17:52,710 --> 00:17:54,850
I went to her room to find a route for her.

376
00:17:54,850 --> 00:17:56,750
But she was so angry.

377
00:17:57,240 --> 00:17:57,900
That was the first time

378
00:17:57,900 --> 00:17:59,300
