396
00:19:16,890 --> 00:19:18,170
You crazy?

397
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:26,050
Princess,

398
00:19:27,090 --> 00:19:28,560
I want to see

399
00:19:28,950 --> 00:19:30,480
